{"tid":618363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對另一半好好 最後佢話對另一個男仔有好感","createTime":"2018-04-05T18:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T19:26:18.000Z","uid":162186,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f18b26833ee200e4be648f6a4bf5af7f3d5786cb","tid":618363,"uid":162186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"自問自己能力範圍內做到既野都做曬<br />\n<br />\n脾氣自問唔差，從來都無鬧過你，次次你發脾氣就算你唔岩都好最後都係我讓步，買野食氹你開心<br />\n<br />\n你返工既野我幫你做，有時lunch做下外賣仔，病左陪你睇醫生，你同屋企人去旅行，我唱錢幫你plan埋行程，買埋電話卡<br />\n<br />\n以為自己拎個心出黎對人，對方會感受到，最後人地對你係地底泥，同你講對另個男仔有好感<br />\n<br />\n呻完，真係好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb14766d685fdb1f325bce4e8b177513ac66c140","tid":618363,"uid":28816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:32:12.000Z","msg":"你只不過是工具人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3976613c4ce1550cc5beb6cc4f56115ef57b0a9","tid":618363,"uid":162186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"其實有時付出咁多 真係好累<br />\n但見到佢個開心樣覺得咩都值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f95f6a6bd1bf9e6295422158b373f29e7aec324","tid":618363,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"男女朋友？"},{"pid":"bfbf5052eaad027c6c47ada57c2354548b264b6e","tid":618363,"uid":61962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f54bac1b65cfe7dc4847f2c3792f50cddf4fb8","tid":618363,"uid":162186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f95f6a6bd1bf9e6295422158b373f29e7aec324","tid":618363,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"男女朋友？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:39:51.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"09fd37bc7ce4f745ac3f02535db9323b93b14961","tid":618363,"uid":106304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:43:23.000Z","msg":"啱啊 好似我自己出post咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係令到我懷疑係咪要做個衰人先好<br />\n明明自己拎個心出嚟對人 最後人地不斷踐踏你嘅好心 都唔緊要 仲要再加以傷害<br />\n經過一段時間嘅沉澱 我都係想繼續真誠待人 希望d仆街遲早俾其他仆街玩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88c5c64bbe6f95aa9829c4b46a1862163c8d07a","tid":618363,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb14766d685fdb1f325bce4e8b177513ac66c140","tid":618363,"uid":28816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:32:12.000Z","msg":"你只不過是工具人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:49:08.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbb329be88470637b85bf6c54943b8a04098ffe","tid":618363,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3976613c4ce1550cc5beb6cc4f56115ef57b0a9","tid":618363,"uid":162186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"其實有時付出咁多 真係好累<br />\n但見到佢個開心樣覺得咩都值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:49:54.000Z","msg":"你開唔開心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e74dec99ed3d02b3d2fdbcd8b3202c17652e74e","tid":618363,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"攞個心出黎攞舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403764d0fbb8fa2cb98e9e6e9c273a7d2c1e8dff","tid":618363,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T18:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攞個心出黎換舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"dfebaeb56b74bf7a2c11adebd3913c2a582c4426","tid":618363,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T19:26:18.000Z","msg":"其實一開始就無鍾意你 同你一齊只係純粹